    "_fontFamily": "Arial",
    "_isSystemFontUsed": true,
    "_N$string": "Example: Convert 13 to binary\n13 / 2 = 6 remainder 1\n6 / 2 = 3 remainder 0\n3 / 2 = 1 remainder 1\n1 / 2 = 0 remainder 1\nRead remainders from bottom up: 1101\nSo, 13 in binary = 1101",
